What is the software?

The software is a 3D platformer, With a player, platforms and a first-person view. The player will be controlled by the user through the ‘W’ ‘S’ ‘A’ and ‘D’ keys (and/or the arrow keys) as well as the ‘space’ key. The camera will be positioned inside the 

Requirements: 
A User-controlled player
Jumping, super jumping and moving function
Floating platforms
A “You failed” screen
A “You win’ screen
Collectables (to win the game)
First-person camera, that moves with the player
Wall running function(maybe)




